參考書目 References
	    一、導論
Frederickson, H. George. 2005. “Whatever Happened to Public Administration?  Governance, Governance Everywhere.” in Evan Ferlie, Lawrence E. Lynn, and Christopher Pollitt, eds., The Oxford Handbook of Public Management. N.Y.: Oxford University Press, pp. 282-304.
Pierre, Jon & B. Guy Peters. 2000. Governance, Politics and the State. Basingstoke: Macmillan.
Rhodes, R. A. W. 1997. Understanding Governance: Policy Networks, Governance, Reflexivity and Accountability. Buckingham: Open University Press.
二、台灣地方治理
呂育誠，2005，〈地方治理意函及制度建立策略之研究-兼論我國縣市推動地方治理的問題與前景〉，《公共行政學報》，第14期，1-38頁。
江大樹，2006，《邁向地方治理》，臺北：元照。
李永展、藍逸之，2002，〈全球化、地方經濟發展與永續性：一個地方資本重建的初論〉，《規劃學報》，第29期，頁17-37。
趙永茂，2007，〈從地方治理論台灣地方發展的基本問題〉，《政治科學論叢》，第31期，頁1-38。
三、兩岸地方治理比較
何增科、王海、舒耕德，2007，〈中國地方治理改革、政治參與和政治合法性初探〉，《經濟社會體制比較》，第132期，69-77頁。
陳剩勇、馬斌，2007，〈民間商會與地方治理：功能及其限度—溫州異地商會的個案研究〉，《社會科學》，第4期， 58-71頁。
紀俊臣，2009，〈兩岸地方治理之比較〉，《中國地方自治》，62(5)：5-18。
高永光，2004，〈地方民主與地方治理〉，財團法人國家政策研究基金會」國政研究報告，http://old.npf.org.tw/PUBLICATION/CL/093/CL-R-093-008.htm
四、東亞地方治理比較
Forrest, Ray. 2009. “Managing the Chaotic City-Social Cohesion: New Forms of Urban Governance and the Challenge for East Asia.” In Ka Ho Mok & Ray Forrest, eds. Changing Governance and Public Policy in East Asia. London: Routledge, pp. 287-303.
Shah, Anwar & Sana Shah. 2006. “The New Vision of Local Governance and the Evolving Roles of Local Governments.” In Anwar Shah, ed. Local Governance in Developing Countries. Washington, D.C.: World Bank Publications , pp.33-78.
五、歐盟地方治理比較
Denters, Bas & Lawrence E. Rose. 2005. “Towards Local Governance.” In Bas Denters & Lawrence E. Rose, eds. Comparing Local Governance: Trends and Developments. N.Y.: Palgrave MacMillan, pp. 246-262.
Marks, Gary & Liesbet Hooghe. 2004. “Contrasting Visions of Multi-level Governance.” In Ian Bache & Matthew Flinders, eds., Multi-level Governance. N.Y: Oxford University Press, pp. 15-30.
Shah, Anwar. 2006. “A Comparative Institutional Framework for Responsive for Responsive, Responsible, and Accountable Local Governance.” In Anwar Shah, ed. Local Governance in Industrial Countries. Washington, D.C.: World Bank Publications, pp. 1-40.
六、拉美地方治理
Lindert, Paul van & Otto Verkoren. 2010. “Local Governance and Local Development in Latin America: Views from Above and Below.” In Paul van Lindert & Otto Verkoren, eds. Decentralized Development in Latin America: Experiences in Local Governance and Local Development. Dordrecht: Springer Science+Business Media B.V, pp. 1-22.
Riggirozzi Pia & Jean Grugel. 2009. “Governance after Neoliberalism.” In Jean Grugel & Pia Riggirozzi. Eds. Governance after Neoliberalism in Latin America. N.Y.: Palgrave Macmillanr, pp. 217-230.
Selee, Andrew. 2004. “Exploring the Link between Decentralization and Democratic Governance.” In Joseph S. Tulchin & Andrew Selee, eds. Decentralization and Democratic Governance in Latin America.  Washington, D.C.: Woodrow Wilson International Center, pp. 3-36.
七、地方公民社會比較
Hermoso, Jocelyn Clare R. & Carmen Geanina Luca. 2006. “Civil Society’s Role in Promoting Local Development in Countries in Transition A comparative study of the Philippines and Romania Development in countries in transition: A comparative study of the Philippines and Romania.” International Social Work International Social Work, 49(3): 319-332.
Sellers, Jefferey M. & Sun-young Kwak, 2011. “State and Society in Local Governance: Lessons from a Multilevel Comparison.” International Journal of Urban and Regional Research, 35(3): 620-643.
八、地方環境治理比較
Lee, R. & Ellen Stokes. 2009. “Environmental Governance: Reconnecting the Global and Local.” Journal of Law and Society, 36(1): 1-10.
Arentsen, Maarten. 2008. “Environmental Governance in a Multilevel Institutional Setting”  Energy and Environment, 19(6): 779-787.
Mol, Arthur P. J. & Sander van den Burg. 2004. “Local Governance of Environmental Flows in Global Modernity.” Local Environment, 9(4): 317–324.
九、地方治理與地方政治
Lubell, Mark Richard, C. Feiock, Edgar E. Ramirez de la Cruz. 2009. “Local Institutions and the Politics of Urban Growth American Journal of Political Science, 53(3), July, Pp. 649–665.
Dannestam Tove. 2008. “Rethinking Local Politics: Towards a Cultural Political Economy of Entrepreneurial Cities.” Space and Polity, 12(3): 353–372.    

備註 Remarks





基本素養 Basic Literacy
□ 人文素養
提升學生之人文素養 Spirit  of Humanism
■ 公民素養
培育具有良善公民素質之人才 Civic Concern
■ 社會關懷
提升學生關懷社會的意識 Social Concern
□ 國際視野
拓展學生之國際視野與國際觀 Global Vision
 

核心能力 Competence
□ 專業與跨域能力
廣博而嚴謹的政治與社會科學訓練 Professional and Interdisciplinary Abilities
■ 思考與判斷能力
掌握時勢脈動並深入瞭解特定議題 Critical Thinking Abilities
□ 語文與溝通能力
強化英語文之訓練與溝通能力 Language Proficiency and Communication Abilities
■ 創新與領導能力
培養學生獨立思考與領導之能力 Innovative and Leadership Abilities
 

課程概述 Course Description
       1. 掌握社會科學重要發展趨勢；
2. 建立比較的宏觀視野，避免陷入單一文化思維；
3. 強化專業英文閱讀及摘要能力；
4. 提升公共管理能力；
5. 掌握地方發展核心議題：
6. 累積獨立研究能力及條件(credit)，有助於申請國內外研究所
 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    1. 掌握社會科學重要發展趨勢；
2. 建立比較的宏觀視野，避免陷入單一文化思維；
3. 強化專業英文閱讀及摘要能力；
4. 提升公共管理能力；
5. 掌握地方發展核心議題：
6. 累積獨立研究能力及條件(credit)，有助於申請國內外研究所。    

